WEBVTT

00:01:01.780 --> 00:01:02.600
Forget it.

00:01:03.240 --> 00:01:04.730
Let's just say I owe them.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:43.440
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:46.470
[Episode 29]

00:02:48.650 --> 00:02:53.300
[Feikun Palu Temple]

00:03:38.900 --> 00:03:40.579
The auspicious time has come.

00:03:40.810 --> 00:03:42.590
Great Feikun Balu,

00:03:42.590 --> 00:03:44.780
Please accept your bride.

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.560
Why is it a man?

00:03:50.710 --> 00:03:52.010
Never seen someone big-boned?

00:03:52.010 --> 00:03:53.480
You are not part of the clan.

00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:54.540
Where is the bride?

00:03:54.780 --> 00:03:56.010
Where is she?

00:03:56.310 --> 00:03:57.740
I am the bride.

00:04:06.970 --> 00:04:09.180
I am thousands of times better than her.

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:09.970
Tell me.

00:04:10.590 --> 00:04:12.120
Where is my divine husband?

00:05:13.660 --> 00:05:14.160
Gosh...

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.160
Attack their limbs!

00:07:44.420 --> 00:07:46.110
We have to kill the big one.

00:07:55.220 --> 00:07:55.890
If it were the chief,

00:07:55.890 --> 00:07:56.820
What would he do?

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:07.400
I can at least borrow this, right?

00:08:07.400 --> 00:08:08.130
Hand it over!

00:08:11.370 --> 00:08:12.860
So what I picked up wasn't trash

00:08:12.860 --> 00:08:14.190
But the chief's weapon.

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:20.560
I can't just have an arrow without a bow.

00:08:26.110 --> 00:08:27.640
Whatever, I'll just try it.

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:06.400
Useless thing.

00:09:27.050 --> 00:09:27.910
Zhang Qianjun!

00:09:28.390 --> 00:09:29.410
You have no sense of direction!

00:09:29.410 --> 00:09:30.740
Who are you to be a guide?

00:09:32.180 --> 00:09:33.640
What's with all the noise?

00:09:35.920 --> 00:09:37.650
S-Sorry for intruding.

00:09:45.460 --> 00:09:46.320
Zhang Qianjun!

00:09:46.330 --> 00:09:47.060
The bow!

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:49.360
What?

00:09:49.870 --> 00:09:50.670
The bow!

00:10:11.980 --> 00:10:13.770
Feikun Balu?

00:10:15.260 --> 00:10:16.780
Feikun Balu?

00:10:18.330 --> 00:10:19.610
Feikun Balu!

00:10:39.670 --> 00:10:40.990
What a piece of work.

00:10:57.960 --> 00:10:59.020
Lend me some blood.

00:11:00.770 --> 00:11:02.260
H-How do I give it to you?

00:11:03.780 --> 00:11:04.530
Watch out!

00:11:50.510 --> 00:11:52.200
Having so much fun without me?

00:12:00.860 --> 00:12:01.840
Bastard,

00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:03.420
I'll kill you!

00:12:16.090 --> 00:12:17.420
What's with the outfit?

00:12:19.310 --> 00:12:20.580
I got married in my spare time,

00:12:20.580 --> 00:12:21.910
And the groom is a loser.

00:12:22.770 --> 00:12:24.670
You have pretty terrible taste then.

00:12:24.670 --> 00:12:26.200
You picked the ugliest one.

00:12:36.340 --> 00:12:37.660
This is the bow left by the chief.

00:12:37.660 --> 00:12:39.590
Shoot its weak spot, and it'll die.

00:13:08.410 --> 00:13:09.210
Zhang Hailou!

00:13:09.950 --> 00:13:10.980
Zhang Qianjun!

00:13:27.290 --> 00:13:27.890
Shrimpie!

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:30.840
Shrimpie!

00:13:38.150 --> 00:13:39.550
Aren't you the one going?

00:13:40.160 --> 00:13:41.050
You go.

00:13:43.730 --> 00:13:44.190
Well...

00:13:44.190 --> 00:13:45.410
It's better if we go together.

00:13:45.410 --> 00:13:47.040
My leg hasn't fully healed yet.

00:13:47.040 --> 00:13:48.090
What if I die?

00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:52.890
What if I die?

00:13:58.820 --> 00:14:00.490
Then I'll give you a grand funeral.

00:14:00.490 --> 00:14:02.420
Then I'll give you a grand funeral.

00:14:07.130 --> 00:14:07.710
Fine.

00:15:11.940 --> 00:15:13.000
Because right now,

00:15:13.220 --> 00:15:14.320
If he thinks

00:15:14.340 --> 00:15:16.300
He can still be with you like before,

00:15:16.300 --> 00:15:17.640
The good in him

00:15:18.930 --> 00:15:20.150
Still has a reason to survive.

00:15:20.150 --> 00:15:22.170
But if you've already started to hate him,

00:15:22.170 --> 00:15:23.770
Or if he comes to believe that

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:24.600
The good in him

00:15:24.600 --> 00:15:26.370
Is hopeless,

00:15:27.430 --> 00:15:30.090
Then that goodness will disappear completely.

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:33.000
He will become an evil spirit from hell.

00:15:34.550 --> 00:15:35.170
So,

00:15:36.250 --> 00:15:38.110
You must act as if nothing

00:15:38.940 --> 00:15:40.330
Has happened.

00:16:14.980 --> 00:16:15.550
What are you doing?

00:16:15.550 --> 00:16:16.550
Get out of the way!

00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:22.600
She tried to kill me first.

00:16:22.750 --> 00:16:23.680
Why did you...

00:16:24.220 --> 00:16:24.980
Who is this?

00:16:25.370 --> 00:16:29.170
-My enemy who wiped out Phoenix Fortress! -My bro from the Archives.

00:16:34.550 --> 00:16:36.140
I will make you pay in blood!

00:16:39.270 --> 00:16:40.610
That didn't kill it?

00:16:42.290 --> 00:16:42.890
Shrimpie!

00:16:55.510 --> 00:16:56.100
Come out!

00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:59.460
Come out and fight me one-on-one!

00:17:37.660 --> 00:17:38.320
Brother?

00:17:40.180 --> 00:17:41.410
Why are you here?

00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:46.500
It's probably because when the priest

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:47.940
Was collecting corpses,

00:17:47.960 --> 00:17:50.560
He brought Great Golden Blade's remains here.

00:18:13.710 --> 00:18:15.110
They can protect themselves.

00:18:15.110 --> 00:18:16.920
The tricky one is here with us.

00:18:17.720 --> 00:18:19.140
This thing already has its vital point blown out.

00:18:19.140 --> 00:18:20.270
Why isn't it dead?

00:18:20.570 --> 00:18:22.200
This seems to be a female snake.

00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:24.310
A female snake's vital point is different from other snakes'.

00:18:24.310 --> 00:18:25.010
Find it

00:18:25.660 --> 00:18:26.520
And destroy it.

00:18:34.470 --> 00:18:35.070
I'll do it.

00:18:52.220 --> 00:18:53.280
What are you doing?

00:18:56.180 --> 00:18:57.110
What should we do?

00:18:57.110 --> 00:18:59.450
Pull the black-haired snake out of its limbs.

00:18:59.450 --> 00:19:00.860
The female snake will naturally spit it out

00:19:00.860 --> 00:19:02.920
When it's unable to control its body.

00:19:03.510 --> 00:19:05.210
Sorry, bro.

00:21:07.460 --> 00:21:08.200
Shrimpie!

00:21:08.510 --> 00:21:09.220
Shrimpie!

00:21:09.700 --> 00:21:10.310
Shrimpie!

00:21:20.740 --> 00:21:21.460
Shrimpie!

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:23.430
Shrimpie!

00:21:24.850 --> 00:21:25.530
Shrimpie.

00:21:38.940 --> 00:21:40.470
Am I going to die here today?

00:21:47.310 --> 00:21:48.210
Shrimpie!

00:22:13.680 --> 00:22:14.680
Hope this works.

00:22:15.700 --> 00:22:16.700
Hopefully...

00:22:28.220 --> 00:22:29.020
Zhang Hailou!

00:22:29.980 --> 00:22:30.900
Shoot!

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:33.100
It's Shrimpie.

00:23:01.770 --> 00:23:02.420
Shrimpie.

00:23:04.070 --> 00:23:04.810
Shrimpie!

00:23:06.740 --> 00:23:07.420
Shrimpie.

00:23:22.870 --> 00:23:24.200
I thought you were dead.

00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:34.280
I had to dodge your blood.

00:23:47.010 --> 00:23:47.810
What's wrong?

00:24:06.720 --> 00:24:07.520
I'm too tired.

00:24:08.400 --> 00:24:09.590
I originally thought my 10 years in Nanyang

00:24:09.590 --> 00:24:11.200
Was already the limit.

00:24:17.270 --> 00:24:19.770
Why did you pick such an ugly piece of clothing?

00:24:19.770 --> 00:24:21.970
It's better than the last one, isn't it?

00:24:23.250 --> 00:24:23.720
I didn't expect it to be even more tiring

00:24:23.720 --> 00:24:25.580
After returning to the Archives.

00:24:27.720 --> 00:24:29.610
Why can my arrow track your blood?

00:24:29.860 --> 00:24:31.260
The tattoos on our bodies

00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:32.910
Appear when our blood is hot.

00:24:33.330 --> 00:24:35.480
Although we got tattoos and became members of the Zhang family,

00:24:35.480 --> 00:24:37.050
We got different Qiongqi tattoos

00:24:37.050 --> 00:24:38.510
And used different herbs.

00:24:38.940 --> 00:24:39.790
Over time,

00:24:39.790 --> 00:24:41.030
It will also affect our respective bodies

00:24:41.030 --> 00:24:42.040
And blood.

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:43.590
Simply put,

00:24:43.590 --> 00:24:44.770
The herbs turned your blood

00:24:44.770 --> 00:24:45.760
Into Yang blood

00:24:45.940 --> 00:24:48.010
And mine into Yin blood.

00:24:49.290 --> 00:24:51.050
And because of a certain substance in the herbs,

00:24:51.050 --> 00:24:53.710
These two types of blood can attract each other.

00:24:54.400 --> 00:24:55.420
And that bow probably

00:24:55.420 --> 00:24:56.530
Used the blood of the Zhang family

00:24:56.530 --> 00:24:57.440
To attack.

00:24:57.660 --> 00:24:59.660
The chief probably also has Yang blood,

00:24:59.660 --> 00:25:01.460
Which is why you can use that bow.

00:25:08.900 --> 00:25:11.030
And Mentor wants me to be the Director?

00:25:11.110 --> 00:25:12.640
You should be the Director.

00:25:12.920 --> 00:25:14.070
My knowledge of the Archives

00:25:14.070 --> 00:25:15.800
Is not even one-tenth of yours.

00:25:21.080 --> 00:25:21.810
Actually, I was only

00:25:21.810 --> 00:25:23.470
10% sure we could win just now.

00:25:24.590 --> 00:25:25.990
I was just giving it a try.

00:25:29.160 --> 00:25:30.570
The Zhang family is really ruthless,

00:25:30.570 --> 00:25:32.230
Inventing a weapon like this.

00:25:32.250 --> 00:25:33.350
With that weapon,

00:25:33.570 --> 00:25:35.700
You killing me would be a piece of cake.

00:25:39.850 --> 00:25:41.740
If I get hurt, even just a little bit,

00:25:41.740 --> 00:25:43.330
You can kill me very easily.

00:25:55.460 --> 00:25:56.320
You were right.

00:25:57.790 --> 00:25:58.860
About what?

00:25:59.420 --> 00:26:01.480
Didn't you ask me before if I was sick?

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:05.400
Something is indeed wrong with my body.

00:26:10.570 --> 00:26:12.380
But I've made peace with myself.

00:26:18.570 --> 00:26:19.290
Shrimpie.

00:26:20.350 --> 00:26:21.200
It's okay.

00:26:22.270 --> 00:26:23.220
If you are sick,

00:26:23.260 --> 00:26:24.720
We can just get it treated.

00:26:26.900 --> 00:26:28.630
I think I'm fine the way I am now.

00:26:30.270 --> 00:26:32.400
I also know why you used to be so strong.

00:26:33.680 --> 00:26:35.540
Because once you start fighting,

00:26:35.830 --> 00:26:37.630
You don't care if you live or die,

00:26:37.920 --> 00:26:39.120
Or about anyone else.

00:26:45.180 --> 00:26:46.350
Now I can do it too.

00:26:49.420 --> 00:26:50.900
It feels pretty good.

00:26:54.180 --> 00:26:55.310
I am very happy now.

00:26:56.440 --> 00:26:57.110
Shrimpie.

00:27:00.810 --> 00:27:01.610
Let's get you treated.

00:27:01.610 --> 00:27:03.150
I killed people. You saw it.

00:27:03.180 --> 00:27:03.810
I know.

00:27:03.850 --> 00:27:05.650
Curing me won't bring them back.

00:27:27.060 --> 00:27:28.390
You have no idea

00:27:28.440 --> 00:27:29.420
What I've done.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:36.690
All right.

00:27:38.810 --> 00:27:39.810
Come with me then.

00:27:42.790 --> 00:27:44.750
I'll show you something good.

00:28:37.270 --> 00:28:38.590
Will you kill me?

00:29:46.770 --> 00:29:48.240
I killed all of them.

00:29:50.490 --> 00:29:51.640
Don't you care?

00:30:56.790 --> 00:30:58.520
Didn't you say you didn't care?

00:31:04.460 --> 00:31:05.920
Your expression right now

00:31:07.940 --> 00:31:09.250
Says otherwise.

00:31:52.570 --> 00:31:53.970
You are just like Mentor.

00:31:54.810 --> 00:31:57.010
You say you don't care what I've become,

00:31:58.340 --> 00:32:01.140
But actually, you can't accept me like this at all.

00:32:04.160 --> 00:32:05.310
You saw Mentor?

00:32:07.740 --> 00:32:08.780
Come out.

00:32:20.420 --> 00:32:21.400
Mentor.

00:32:32.680 --> 00:32:34.680
You've been following me all along.

00:32:35.590 --> 00:32:36.940
What do you want?

00:32:47.110 --> 00:32:48.330
Just kill me.

00:32:49.980 --> 00:32:52.690
Didn't you say you'd handle it yourself?

00:32:54.140 --> 00:32:54.940
Mentor,

00:33:01.370 --> 00:33:02.450
I thought I could.

00:33:04.660 --> 00:33:05.810
But I can't.

00:33:08.070 --> 00:33:09.350
I want to kill people.

00:33:10.920 --> 00:33:12.310
I can't control myself.

00:33:14.810 --> 00:33:16.530
I'm really going crazy.

00:33:27.140 --> 00:33:29.070
If I had known it would be like this,

00:33:31.030 --> 00:33:33.290
You might as well have killed me that day.

00:33:36.570 --> 00:33:38.430
At least I could have died at home.

00:34:03.340 --> 00:34:04.990
These things

00:34:05.920 --> 00:34:07.680
Can be made into a medicine.

00:34:11.820 --> 00:34:13.350
It can stabilize your mind.

00:34:30.380 --> 00:34:32.360
So it's because of this medicine

00:34:34.760 --> 00:34:36.340
That you became like this?

00:34:40.030 --> 00:34:41.690
Go make the medicine quickly,

00:34:42.770 --> 00:34:44.270
And end all of this.

00:35:36.050 --> 00:35:38.310
The medicine Mentor traded her life for,

00:35:38.320 --> 00:35:39.720
I burned it in front of her

00:35:40.000 --> 00:35:41.360
With my own hands.

00:35:43.000 --> 00:35:44.900
Mentor's expression—

00:35:46.570 --> 00:35:47.780
She looked so sad,

00:35:49.130 --> 00:35:50.800
But it was so amusing to me.

00:35:57.770 --> 00:36:00.300
It would have been great if you were there too.

00:36:10.010 --> 00:36:10.880
Zhang Haixia,

00:36:12.770 --> 00:36:14.180
You're crazy!

00:36:22.780 --> 00:36:24.500
Didn't you know that already?

